<plot>Only four episodes of this show about young, unmarried Daniel Boone were shown. Boone does his exploring with three companions, Peter Dawes, a 12-year-old English boy; Hawk, a runaway slave; and Tsiskwa, a Cherokee Indian. Meanwhile, Rebecca Bryan waits at home hoping that she and Daniel will marry.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?666948</url></doc>
